'''CCTV-2''' is the [[finance]] (formerly [[economy]] until August 24, 2009) focused channel of the [[China Central Television|CCTV]] (China Central Television) Network in the [[People's Republic of China]].
The primary concerns of this channel include: * [[Energy conservation]] * [[Stock exchange]] * [[Scams]] (Buyer Beware) * Finance and consumer related [[game shows]]
